class mything.Log(init=None)¶

A Log Class. Just append to the log and we take care of the timing. You can set the format of the time.

Note

This function is not suitable for sending spam e-mails.

append(message, status=None, settings=None)¶

append the current message to the log using the time of the call

Args:

  • message (_type_): The message to be logged.

  • status (_type_, optional): a tag good for automatic ientification of status, for example ERROR or DONE. Defaults to None.

  • settings (_type_, optional): a dictoinary of options. Defaults to None.
